An RNG simulator. A cathartic shrine to suffering.
Click buttons. Watch numbers betray you. Feel validated.

[b]Why does it exist?[/b]
To expose just how cursed your luck really is—with data, not just vibes.
Also: because I thought it’d be funny.

[b]Core Concepts:[/b]

Every roll is tracked.

TODO: Failure increases your success odds (pity scaling). Customizable.

