[b]Terms Glossary:[/b]

Z-score: Statistical measure of how far a result strays from average.

Anomaly: A run of improbability too bold to ignore.

Blast Cap: Max number of rolls per batch (safety first).

Merp Mode: Randomized passive rolling. It's fine. Probably. When its implemented...

